ELDEN RING · ER — the Lands Between catalogued (an unofficial fan tribute)
Copyright (c) 2026 David Lee Wise (ROOT0) / TriPod LLC — for the original commentary,
catalogue, design, the ACI/.dlw badges, and presentation ONLY.

Elden Ring is the creation of FROMSOFTWARE, Inc. (directed by Hidetaka Miyazaki, with
worldbuilding by George R. R. Martin), © FromSoftware / Bandai Namco Entertainment.
This project is an UNOFFICIAL HOMAGE: a catalogue with original commentary and ACI
badge-work. NO game text, art, or assets are reproduced; quotation is avoided in favour
of original description.

Elden Ring's lore is deliberately ambiguous and contested; what is sealed here is a
READING of it — hedged where the game itself hedges — not asserted canon. "The
Elementals" and "The Eternals" are this catalogue's own organizing frame.

Character, place, and concept names (Marika, Ranni, the Erdtree, the Lands Between,
the Tarnished, etc.) are the intellectual property of FromSoftware / Bandai Namco,
used here for identification and commentary under fair-use principles.

